						<p><hi rend="bold">Undated. (11th cent. A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>Fragment and built in at the top and damaged. Seems to record a sale of wet land and the <hi rend="italic">sabhā</hi> of Nālūr remitted the taxes by receiving 12 <hi rend="italic">kācus</hi> from three individuals from the locality.</p>						

